臭名昭著的大人物的遗产管理机构就标志性照片提起的诉讼达成和解https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-notorious-bi-gs-estate-settles-lawsuit-over-iconic-photos-3574509?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-notorious-bi-gs-遗产诉讼就标志性照片达成和解Elizabeth AubreySun, 21 Jan 2024 19:25:34 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3574509 <p><img width="2000" height="1272" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="臭名昭著的大佬" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-800x509.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-696x443.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “未经我们客户的许可，克里斯托弗的照片不得用于商业用途”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-notorious-b-i-gs-estate-settles-lawsuit-over-iconic-photos-3574509">The Notorious BIG 的遗产管理机构就标志性照片提起的诉讼达成和解的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1272" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="臭名昭著的大佬" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-800x509.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-696x443.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G-Photo-by-Catherine-McGann_Getty-Images-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-notorious-big">臭名昭著的大人物的</a>遗产管理机构已就这位已故说唱歌手在世贸中心的一些标志性照片提起的诉讼达成和解。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-notoroious-b-i-g-ready-to-die-25-9-surprising-things-era-defining-album-2546691">Notorious BIG 的“Ready To Die”（25 点）：关于这张定义时代的专辑的 9 个令人惊讶的事情</a></strong></li></ul><p>1996年，已故摄影师Chi Modu拍摄了Biggie——真名Christopher Wallace的照片。这些照片显示这位说唱歌手在世贸中心塔楼前，拍摄于 9 月 11 日纽约市袭击事件五年前。</p><p>在 2019 年提起最初诉讼时，Biggie 的遗产管理机构声称 Modu 非法许可这些照片用于浴帘和 NFT 等物品，“完全无视 BIG 的权利”。这位摄影师于 2021 年去世。</p><p> 2022 年，一名法官裁定，以这种方式在此类商品上使用的图像确实可能侵犯了说唱歌手的肖像权。</p><p>本周， <em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/business/legal/notorious-big-estate-settles-lawsuit-chi-modu-world-trade-center-image-1235585210/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《公告牌》</a></em>报道称，The Notorious BIG 遗产管理机构的代表 Staci Jennifer Trager 宣布，已于 1 月 18 日就该诉讼达成和解。 </p><figure id="attachment_3574510" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3574510" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3574510" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G.-Photo-by-Clarence-Davis_NY-Daily-News-Archive-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="臭名昭著的 B.I.G." width="2000" height="1272" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G.-Photo-by-Clarence-Davis_NY-Daily-News-Archive-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G.-Photo-by-Clarence-Davis_NY-Daily-News-Archive-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G.-Photo-by-Clarence-Davis_NY-Daily-News-Archive-via-Getty-Images-800x509.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G.-Photo-by-Clarence-Davis_NY-Daily-News-Archive-via-Getty-Images-696x443.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G.-Photo-by-Clarence-Davis_NY-Daily-News-Archive-via-Getty-Images-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Notorious-B.I.G.-Photo-by-Clarence-Davis_NY-Daily-News-Archive-via-Getty-Images-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3574510" class="wp-caption-text">臭名昭著的大人物 - 图片来源：Clarence Davis/NY Daily News Archive via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>虽然和解协议的条款尚未公开，但特拉格表示，该协议是由比吉的孩子和莫杜的遗孀达成的，他们都是已故艺术家遗产的执行人。<br /> “未经我们客户的许可，克里斯托弗的照片不能用于商业用途，”特拉格说。 “和解协议证明了我们的客户以及我们的团队成员多年来坚持到底的奉献精神。”<br /> <em>NME</em>已联系 Modu 代表征求意见。<br /> Modu 多年来拍摄了许多嘻哈巨星的照片，在 2011 年的一次采访中，他表示在世贸中心拍摄的灵感来自于 Biggie 的歌曲《Juicy》中的歌词。<br /> “当我想到要代表 Notorious BIG 扮演纽约之王时，我想还有什么比以两座典型的纽约市建筑为背景更好的背景呢，”莫杜说。 “这个形象仍然新鲜，有助于进一步让这些偶像在一代人的心中永垂不朽。”<br />去年，宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/a-notorious-b-i-g-nft-collection-will-include-the-right-to-license-an-iconic-freestyle-he-delivered-at-17-3253873">将与 Notorious BIG 的遗产管理机构合作发行一系列 NFT，其中包括这位说唱歌手青少年时期的标志性自由泳的许可权。</a></p><p> <em>Sky&#39;s the Limit: The Notorious BIG Collection，</em>包括受 Biggie 启发的 3D NFT 雕像人物。购买其中之一的每个人都将获得自由风格音频的许可权，这是 BIG 17 岁时在布鲁克林 Bed-Stuy 的街角说唱的。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-notorious-b-i-gs-estate-settles-lawsuit-over-iconic-photos-3574509">The Notorious BIG 的遗产管理机构就标志性照片提起的诉讼达成和解的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
